headline: Aon (AON) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript
summary: The financial presentation, which Edmund will reference in his remarks, is posted on our website.  2025 was a year of great strategic progress and performance milestones for Aon.  Among the highlights, we advanced the disciplined execution of our three-by-three plan, which continues to accelerate our Aon United strategy by further integrating risk capital and human capital, expanding Aon client leadership, and leveraging Aon business services to drive greater capability, innovation, and efficiency.

headline: Aon: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: DUBLIN (AP) — Aon PLC (AON) on Friday reported fourth-quarter net income of $1.69 billion. On a per-share basis, the Dublin-based company said it had net income of $7.82. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring gains, were $4.85 per share.
